  {%- comment -%} Parent Brand Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-parent section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-parent__grid">
        <div class="about-parent__content">
          <span class="about-parent__label">The Parent Brand</span>
          <h2 class="about-parent__title">Born from 25 Years of Pharmaceutical Excellence</h2>
          <div class="about-parent__text rte">
            <p><strong>PRM Pharmaceuticals</strong> was founded in <strong>1999</strong> in Bhavnagar, Gujarat by <strong>Mr. Hemang Soni</strong>, a first-generation entrepreneur who set out with a single conviction — that quality Indian medicine should be affordable and accessible to every family. The company's very first product, <strong>Corylplus™</strong>, launched the same year, became the foundation stone for what would grow into one of India's respected mid-size pharmaceutical houses.</p>
            <p>Today, PRM Pharma is the <strong>largest player in the Pharma O.T.C. segment</strong> with three decades of market presence — <strong>85+ brands</strong>, <strong>250+ formulations</strong>, <strong>35,000+ satisfied customers</strong>, and a distribution network covering <strong>300+ channels across 28+ Indian states</strong> and <strong>3 international markets</strong>.</p>
            <p>In <strong>2013</strong>, recognising a growing demand for authentic, safety-tested Ayurvedic medicines, PRM Pharmaceuticals launched its Ayurveda and herbal wellness division — <strong>HerboVilla</strong>. The mission was clear: combine the wisdom of <em>ancient Ayurveda</em> with the discipline of <em>modern therapeutics</em>. We call this <strong>"SampurnaSudhha"</strong> — Pure Quality — formulations crafted with high phytoconstituent concentration, manufactured under the same pharmaceutical-grade systems that define our allopathic portfolio.</p>
            <p>In <strong>2020</strong>, the next chapter began as <strong>Dhyey Soni</strong> — Hemang Soni's son and a B. Pharm and M. Finance graduate from <strong>IIT-Delhi</strong> — joined the family business, leading a new era of digital transformation, direct-to-consumer commerce, and modern formulation research grounded in classical Ayurvedic texts.</p>
            <p>Our guiding principle has remained unchanged across two generations: <em>"Extending Healthy Horizons"</em> — to every Indian family today, and to every corner of the globe tomorrow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-parent__links">
            <a href="https://www.prmpharmaceuticals.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--outline btn--small">
              Visit PRM Pharmaceuticals
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-parent__visual">
          <div class="about-parent__card">
            <div class="about-parent__card-head">
              <span class="about-parent__card-logo">PRM<span>Pharma</span></span>
              <span class="about-parent__card-year">Since 1999</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="about-parent__card-list">
              <li><strong>Allopathic</strong> — Core pharmaceutical manufacturing &amp; distribution</li>
              <li><strong>85+ Brands</strong> across therapy areas</li>
              <li><strong>250+ Formulations</strong> in tablets, syrups, capsules, ointments</li>
              <li><strong>28+ States, 3 Countries</strong> of active distribution</li>
              <li><strong>WHO-GMP, ISO 9001:2015</strong> certified facility</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="about-parent__card-divider"><span>Ayurvedic Division</span></div>
            <div class="about-parent__card-child">
              <span class="about-parent__card-logo about-parent__card-logo--child">Herbo<span>Villa</span></span>
              <span class="about-parent__card-year">Since 2013</span>
              <p>Classical Ayurvedic &amp; herbal formulations manufactured to pharmaceutical standards.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Ayurveda Philosophy — 3 Doshas {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-doshas section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-header__label">5,000 Years of Living Wisdom</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">The Philosophy of Ayurveda</h2>
        <p class="section-header__text">Ayurveda — <em>आयुर्वेद</em>, literally "the science of life" — sees every human as a unique balance of three <em>doshas</em>. Every HerboVilla formulation is composed with this balance in mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-doshas__grid">
        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--vata">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <path d="M6 20c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
              <path d="M6 28c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
              <path d="M6 36c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">वात</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Vata</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Air + Ether</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of movement — breath, circulation, thought, impulse. When balanced: creativity, vitality, clarity. When imbalanced: anxiety, dryness, insomnia.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Ashwagandha</span><span>Brahmi</span><span>Licorice</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--pitta">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <path d="M24 6c-6 8-10 14-10 22a10 10 0 0 0 20 0c0-8-4-14-10-22z"/>
              <path d="M20 28c0 4 2 6 4 6s4-2 4-6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">पित्त</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Pitta</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Fire + Water</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of transformation — metabolism, digestion, body heat, intellect. When balanced: sharp focus, strong digestion. When imbalanced: inflammation, acidity, irritability.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Amla</span><span>Neem</span><span>Triphala</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--kapha">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <circle cx="24" cy="30" r="14"/>
              <path d="M24 16c0-6 4-10 4-10s4 4 4 10"/>
              <path d="M16 30c0-3 2-5 4-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">कफ</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Kapha</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Earth + Water</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of structure — stability, lubrication, immunity, endurance. When balanced: calm, strength, resilience. When imbalanced: sluggishness, congestion, weight gain.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Tulsi</span><span>Ginger</span><span>Turmeric</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <p class="about-doshas__footnote">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 2"/></svg>
        Most people are a dual dosha — a blend of two primary energies. Our wellness desk can help you understand your unique constitution.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

